{
  "stem": "16503.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But at least-- it-- it was beyond my comprehension that he would actually look up my father in a SS uniform and come.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I mean, that is-- I haven't heard a story like that from no one.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Were there food shortages?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, there were food shortages.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I really, you know, not-- not-- nothing drastic at that particular time.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm sure we had less meat.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I'm sure we had less fruit.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I'm sure we had less of-- less of stuff, but nothing which clicks my memory, no.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At that time?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not really, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the Germans-- I don't know how it came about and that would have to be by somebody who was much older than me, because he would know the ins and outs.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But at the real end of Prague, there was a playing complex.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, it wasn't even a complex.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was a field where there was a running track.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was tennis courts, which are converted into volleyball courts, and a little wooden shack, which was operational.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they used to have volunteers in it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And in the summer, you could buy a lemonade there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And in the winter, you could buy a hot chocolate there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And what we did there, we congregated there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we ran track and we had gymnastic [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] classes.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the older kids played volleyball.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And that is the place where you finally-- well, I finally came into the Jewish environment of children, older and some younger but not much, and got quite a series of beautiful friendships.",
      "word_count": 33
    }
  ],
